thread.title: Robert

author: Robert
title: Robert
text: Del CIty offers a good line of products, and I have been ordering plenty to support my renovation of a classic car. There's just one point of confusion: Often on the website, you can't tell if you can buy the quantity you need or whether you MUST buy an entire box. In other words the website isn't often clear about the quantities you may purchase. I often fix this by calling their excellent customer service people.
